<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Medical Hub</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #3498db;">
                <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0;">Welcome to Medical Hub</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px;">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello Dear,</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Thank you for registering with our tele-medicine app. We're excited to
                    have you on board and look forward to providing you with quality healthcare services from the
                    comfort of your home.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">You have registered with the following email address: <strong
                        style="color: #3498db;">
                        <%= user_email %>
                    </strong></p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">To get started, please verify your account by clicking the button below:
                </p>
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin: 30px auto;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: #3498db;">
                            <a href="<%= link%>" target="_blank"
                                style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">Verify
                                Your Account</a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to
                    contact our support team.</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Best regards,<br>The Medical Hub Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td
                style="padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #f8f8f8; color: #888888; font-size: 14px;">
                <p style="margin: 0;">&copy; 2024 Medical Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">123 Main St, City, State, ZIP</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>